  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this randomised open study is to examine the effect of self-management program
      for diabetes patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The primary aim in this study is HbA1c in addition to secondary aims like quality of life and
      coping.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
